EmailTemplate.name: Preschool Directors DANCE announcement
EmailTemplate.subject: Announcing Saturday Dance classes for pre-schoolers at SACS!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName}
Greetings from St Andrew's Cathedral School!
We have had a very happy and smooth start the 2014 school year. It has been wonderful to see our new Kindergarten students start 'big' school and settle in so well.
We are very excited to announce a new dance programme on offer at St Andrew's! Pre schoolers can now learn to dance with some of the best dance instructors and choreographers in Australia. DANCE AUSTRALIA is operating from a customised dance studio in St Andrew's House. You don't have to be a student or sibling at SACS - everyone is welcome to join in.
Timetable - Saturdays
9.30am - 10.00am Babies Jazz
10.00am - 10.30am Kindy Ballet (5 - 6 Yrs)
10.30am - 11.00am Kindy Jazz (5 - 6 Yrs)
Class details and contacts are attached. Dance Australia are offering the first class for free! So you can try before you buy. We look forward to welcoming the children of {!Account.Name} to dance classes.
The dance studio is also available for centre bookings if you would like to bring your pre schoolers in for a group lesson. Please contact me to arrange.
In the meantime, SAVE THE DATE! Our Junior School Twilight Tour will be held on Wednesday 2 April at 6.30pm. I will bring along invites when I visit your centre during March.
I look forward to seeing you again during 2014.
Best regards,
Robyn
Robyn Pedley Enrolments Assistant
